  "description": "<p>CNY Event Promoter 年货海产销售员</p><p><br /></p><p>Responsibilities 职责:</p><p>• Promote and handle food products 推销处理食品</p><p>• Receiving of goods 收点货</p><p>• Replenish Stocks 补货</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements 要求:</p><p>• Responsible 负责任</p><p>• Proactive Outgoing 积极的态度和主动</p><p>• Physically Fit 有力气</p><p>• Able to speak both chinese and english to promote to customers 会说中英文推销给客户</p><p><br /></p><p>Others 其他：</p><p>• Training Provided (Fresh graduates welcomed!)</p><p><br /></p><p>Date: 15.01.2026 - 16.02.2026 CNY EVE</p><p>Operating hours: 9.30am to 9.30/10pm (morning/noon/full shift)</p><p>Working Address：62 Smith Street</p><p>Contact 91898878 or email suyi.tam@tamkahsharksfin.com to apply</p><p>Contract for service - fixed hourly pay</p>",
